containing_words.word: 冠狀動脈旁路移植手術

sentences.english: Can also be provided with a by-pass switch, model 8150.
sentences.chinese: 在8150型上還可以配置旁路開關。

sentences.english: You could also embed the sideway approach within the top-down or bottom-up approach.
sentences.chinese: 您也可以在自頂向下或自底向上方法中嵌入旁路方法。

sentences.english: Analysis of the retrograde sequence of AP activation may localize and ablate the APs successfully.
sentences.chinese: 仔細分析旁路逆傳激動順序可以精確定位，成功消蝕。

sentences.english: No person shall override safety interlocks without proper authorization.
sentences.chinese: 任何人不得未經授權旁路安全聯鎖。

sentences.english: Ninety-two atrioventricular (AV) accessory pathways in 90 patients were abolished by catheter radiofrequency current ab-lation.
sentences.chinese: 以射頻電流阻斷90例預激綜合徵患者的房室旁路。

sentences.english: I set it up for lower pressure using a built-in bypass regulator.
sentences.chinese: 我把它較低的壓力，使用內置在旁路調節器。

sentences.english: Right-sided accessory atrioventricular pathways were ablated by radiofrequency current in 6 patients with Wolff-Parkinson-White syndrome.
sentences.chinese: 以射頻電流消融6例預激綜合徵患者的右側旁路。

sentences.english: I looked at the by-pass and walked across it.
sentences.chinese: 我看看那條旁路，從上面走了過去。

sentences.english: Conclusions Coronary sinus diverticulum is anatomically intimately related to the posteroseptal accessory pathway.
sentences.chinese: 結論冠狀靜脈竇憩室與後間隔旁路存在着解剖關係。

sentences.english: This is one incredibly well-made bypass pruner .
sentences.chinese: 這是一個令人難以置信的製作精良的旁路剪。

sentences.english: The internal leakage of low-pressure bypass is a common problem in steam turbine.
sentences.chinese: 低壓旁路的內漏是汽輪機組系統中普遍存在的問題。

sentences.english: The effects of by-pass inductance on the compression were discussed.
sentences.chinese: 給出了旁路電感對壓縮效果的影響。

sentences.english: The bypass line shall be hydraulically sized to accurately measure low flow.
sentences.chinese: 旁路管線應該經過水力分析，能夠精確測量低流量。

sentences.english: There is only one way to the village. No sideway.
sentences.chinese: 只有一條路通向這個村莊，沒有旁路。

sentences.english: The manual bypass switch isolates the inverter output and the static switch for maintenance operations.
sentences.chinese: 手動旁路開關逆變器隔離輸出和維護操作的靜態開關。
